lead_paragraph: Tiger Woods picked up a headache after forgetting his sunglasses in his final practice round on Wednesday but otherwise declared himself good to go as he prepared to bring an end to a 16-month absence from tournament golf.

headline.print_headline: No Shades but Woods 'Ready' for Long-Awaited Comeback
